# IlmBase & OpenEXR
checked_find_package (OpenEXR REQUIRED
                      VERSION_MIN 2.0
                      RECOMMEND_MIN 2.2
                      RECOMMEND_MIN_REASON
                        "OpenEXR 2.2 is the oldest version our CI tests against, and the minimum that supports DWA compression"
